<cb:div>
<pb n="0177a" xml:id="I01.0070.0177a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0177a00" type="honorific"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><cb:docNumber>No. 70</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0177a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>周大將軍延壽公碑頌</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0177a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0177a0101">周
<lb ed="I" n="0177a02" type="honorific"/>大
<lb ed="I" n="0177a03" type="honorific"/>將
<lb ed="I" n="0177a04" type="honorific"/>軍
<lb ed="I" n="0177a05" type="honorific"/>延
<lb ed="I" n="0177a06" type="honorific"/>壽
<lb ed="I" n="0177a07" type="honorific"/>公
<lb ed="I" n="0177a08" type="honorific"/>碑
<lb ed="I" n="0177a09" type="honorific"/>頌</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0177b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0177b0101">夫真源澄寂。沖趣虛玄。非可言寄。會通<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">筌</unclear>致。是以釋迦應生王宮。救昏迷於大□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0177b02" type="honorific"/>娑羅。示群品之無常。自尒迄今。邈餘千載。純風潛遏。道<note n="0177001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB07656"/>＝喪【史】</note><note n="0177001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB07656"/>【佛拓】，喪【史】</note><app n="0177001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">喪</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB07656"/></rdg></app>薨淪。用使凝塵翳於黔□。□
<lb ed="I" n="0177b03" type="honorific"/>垢穢於凡俗。自非識慧幽明。洞監八解。安能樹善<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">因</unclear>於火宅。建般若於冥津矣。使持節
<lb ed="I" n="0177b04" type="honorific"/>大將軍大<note n="0177002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨜞＝都【史】</note><note n="0177002" resp="ihp" type="mod">𨜞【佛拓】，都【史】</note><app n="0177002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">都</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨜞</rdg></app>督勳州汾州絳州晉州建州王<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">葉</unclear>城□□城□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">頭</unclear>城□辟城樂昌城姚襄
<lb ed="I" n="0177b05" type="honorific"/>城諸軍事勳州刺史延壽<note n="0177003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨛦＝郡【史】</note><note n="0177003" resp="ihp" type="mod">𨛦【佛拓】，郡【史】</note><app n="0177003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">郡</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨛦</rdg></app>開國公万紐于寔。志性沈<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">簡</unclear>。器度寬雅。懷仁納□。文翁未
<lb ed="I" n="0177b06" type="honorific"/>必比其能。謙恭節儉。四<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">知</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">焉</unclear>得返其□。受□邊□事□□□□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">夷</unclear>□□望旗<app type="star" corresp="#0177001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">喪</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB07656"/></rdg></app>氣。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">恩</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0177b07" type="honorific"/>被北<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">狄</unclear>。則繈負雲歸。民飲<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">惠</unclear>化。咸詠甘棠之風。人□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">寔</unclear>。咸歌來□之美。<note n="0177004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">㫺＝昔【史】</note><note n="0177004" resp="ihp" type="mod">㫺【佛拓】，昔【史】</note><app n="0177004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">昔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㫺</rdg></app><note n="0177005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30970"/>＝邵【史】</note><note n="0177005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30970"/>【佛拓】，邵【史】</note><app n="0177005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邵</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30970"/></rdg></app>奭翼周。
<lb ed="I" n="0177b08" type="honorific"/>絳侯征漠。方之於今。未足踰也。公雖位亟<note n="0177006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𣅂＝旦【史】</note><note n="0177006" resp="ihp" type="mod">𣅂【佛拓】，旦【史】</note><app n="0177006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">旦</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𣅂</rdg></app>□。□□五<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">等</unclear>。寄意道□。□心妙域。知貪<note n="0177007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">虵＝蛇【史】</note><note n="0177007" resp="ihp" type="mod">虵【佛拓】，蛇【史】</note><app n="0177007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蛇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">虵</rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0177b09" type="honorific"/>如幻。不保全於夙霄。娛遊永夜。豈待明於昧□。□□風防諸貴鄉城耆老。訪地祇洹。式
<lb ed="I" n="0177b10" type="honorific"/>建靈塔。若迺汾水逕其陽。似熙連之□往。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">諒</unclear>山□□北。等耆闍之鬱盛。　皇帝陛下。
<lb ed="I" n="0177b11" type="honorific"/>福洽人天。威加四海。貫萬國於宇宙。納<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">蒼</unclear>生於覆載。□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">大</unclear>冢宰晉國公之勞王□□牟
<lb ed="I" n="0177b12" type="honorific"/>伊<app type="star" corresp="#0177006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">旦</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𣅂</rdg></app>。光讚幽遐。敷<note n="0177008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𢾙＝揚【史】</note><note n="0177008" resp="ihp" type="mod">𢾙【佛拓】，揚【史】</note><app n="0177008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">揚</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𢾙</rdg></app>妙軌。非銘金石。將何以則。不述景行。芳音莫著。睹茲<note n="0177009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𠇾＝休【史】</note><note n="0177009" resp="ihp" type="mod">𠇾【佛拓】，休【史】</note><app n="0177009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">休</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠇾</rdg></app>烈。敢為之
<lb ed="I" n="0177b13" type="honorific"/>頌。
<lb ed="I" n="0177b14" type="honorific"/>曰若稽古。如是我聞。如如本絕。茫茫已分。有佛有法。為皇為君。聖寔廣運。大智普<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">播</unclear>。其
<lb ed="I" n="0177b15" type="honorific"/>溫如日。其慧如雲。道心惟遠。禪念以懃。牢籠軒瑣。影響彌文。有法大士。為王爪臣。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">菩</unclear>登
<lb ed="I" n="0177b16" type="honorific"/>一子。功參十人。情超海岸。道濟河津。開沙兜府。守罔稱神。忠為令<note n="0177010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30677"/>＝德【史】</note><note n="0177010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30677"/>【佛拓】，德【史】</note><app n="0177010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">德</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30677"/></rdg></app>善作福因。弘茲佛
<lb ed="I" n="0177b17" type="honorific"/>日。會此堯辰。丹楹已構。戴壁斯陳。奉資聖帝。成我能仁。
<lb ed="I" n="0177b18" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　　　　大周保定元年歲次辛巳三月壬午朔十日辛卯敬造。</p>
